caption.p: ( a) CVs at a scan rate of 0.1 mV s −1 between 0.01 and 2.5 V (vs. Li +/Li). ( b) The initial five charge/discharge profiles of as-dealloyed Cu 6Sn 5 anode with the current density of 0.1 A g −1. ( c) Ex situ XRD patterns collected at various states. ( d) Cycling performance of the Cu 6Sn 5 at current density of 0.1 A g −1. ( e) The charge–discharge voltage profiles of the Cu 6Sn 5 alloy electrode at various current densities from 0. 1 A g −1 to 2.0 A g −1. ( f) Rate performance at various current densities from 0. 1 A g −1 to 2.0 A g −1.
